cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting max_pdschReferenceSignalPower to an invalid positive value will cause RF power configuration errors and prevent the gNB from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 max_pdschReferenceSignalPower 設定為無效的正值會導致 RF 功率配置錯誤，並阻止 gNB 正確啟動。
